title: UPSC Civil Services Prelims 2024 Notification
content: Union Public Service Commission has released the notification for Civil Services Preliminary Examination 2024. The exam is scheduled for May 26, 2024.
content_summary: Union Public Service Commission has released the notification for Civil Services Preliminary Examination 2024. The exam is scheduled for May 26, 2024.

title: GATE 2024 Admit Card Released
content: GATE 2024 admit cards are now available for download. Candidates can access their admit cards from the official GATE website using their login credentials.
content_summary: GATE 2024 admit cards are now available for download. Candidates can access their admit cards from the official GATE website using their login credentials.

title: JEE Main 2024 Registration Extended
content: The registration deadline for JEE Main 2024 has been extended to December 15, 2023. Students can now register through the official NTA website.
content_summary: The registration deadline for JEE Main 2024 has been extended to December 15, 2023. Students can now register through the official NTA website.
